type.name: Morphite
type.description: Morphite is a highly unorthodox mineral that can only be found in the hard-to-get Mercoxit ore. It is hard to use Morphite as a basic building material, but when it is joined with existing structures it can enhance the performance and durability manifold. This astounding quality makes this the material responsible for ushering in a new age in technology breakthroughs. May be obtained by reprocessing the following ores: 0.0 security status solar system or lower: Mercoxit, Magma Mercoxit, Vitreous Mercoxit
